        " : سَأَلْتُهُ عَنِ اَلْأَحْكَامِ فَقَالَ \"يَجُوزُ عَلَى كُلِّ دَيِّنٍ بِمَا يَسْتَحْلِفُونَ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4319 - Al-Ala narrated from Muhammad ibn Muslim who said: I asked him about oaths. Imam (as) said: \"It is permissible to take an oath with every religious group according to what they regard as binding for oaths.\""
        ]
